    dc:description "Fig. 2. Phlaeopterus species, habitus. A) P. elongatus, male (UAMObs:Ento:232543), B) P. filicornis, female" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102845/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102867>
    dc:description "Fig. 17. Phlaeopterus species. Pronota, dorsal view, of A) P. fusconiger, B) P. frosti, C) P. filicornis, D) P. hatchi, E) P. elongatus. Abdominal segments 4–6, dorsal view, of F) P. houkae, G) P. obsoletus, H) P. elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102867/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102871>
    dc:description "Fig. 20. Phlaeopterus species, mesosterna, ventral oblique view. A) P. longipennis, B) P. obsoletus, C) P. olympicus, D) P. frosti, E) P. occidentalis, F) P. elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102871/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102881>
    dc:description "Fig. 25. Phlaeopterus species, aedeagi (left = ventral view; right = dorsal view of median lobe). A) Phlaeopterus frosti, B) P. hatchi, C) P. filicornis, D) P. elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102887>
    dc:description "Fig. 29. Phlaeopterus species. Right mandibles, ventral view, of A) P. obsoletus, B) P. bakerensis, C) P. elongatus. D) P. bakerensis, humeral angle of elytron, dorsal view. Apices of elytra of E) P. loganensis, F) P. hatchi, G) P. filicornis female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102903>
    dc:description "Fig. 37. Sensory structures on antenna of A) Lesteva pallipes, B–C) Lesteva pubescens, D–E) Unamis sp. undescribed, F–G) Phlaeopterus houkae, H–I) Phlaeopterus obsoletus, J–K) Phlaeopterus elongatus. In B, D, F, H, and J, white boxes indicate inset area that is magnified in the image to the right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102905>
    dc:description "Fig. 39. Phlaeopterus species, maxillae, dorsal and ventral views. A–B) P. houkae, C–D) P. obsoletus, E–F) P. elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102905/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102909>
    dc:description "Fig. 41. Phlaeopterus species, hypopharynges, dorsal view, of A) P. obsoletus, B) P. kavanaughi, C) P. elongatus. D) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, metatrochanter with apical tooth. Heads, ventral view, of E) Lesteva pallipes, F) Lesteva pubescens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5102911>
    dc:description "Fig. 42. Heads, ventral view, of A) Unamis sp. undescribed, B) Unamis sp., C) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, D) Phlaeopterus houkae, E) Phlaeopterus longipennis, F) Phlaeopterus elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102911/files/figure.png" ;
